{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"9d0270d6-12b5-410a-931e-5acb2a02e3b5","content":"No workflow files found in the current directory, so here's general guidance for the switch:\n\n### Changes needed for NuGet Trusted Publishing (OIDC)\n\n**1. NuGet.org setup** — Register your GitHub repo as a trusted publisher:\n- Go to **nuget.org → Manage Packages → [your package] → Trusted publishers**\n- Add your GitHub repository, workflow file name, and (optionally) environment\n\n**2. Workflow changes:**\n\n```yaml\n# Add OIDC permission at job level\njobs:\n  publish:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    permissions:\n      id-token: write   # Required for OIDC token\n      contents: read\n\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      # ... build & pack steps ...\n\n      # Replace your current push step:\n      # OLD:\n      #   dotnet nuget push **/*.nupkg --api-key ${{ secrets.NUGET_API_KEY }} --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n      \n      # NEW:\n      - name: Push to NuGet\n        run: dotnet nuget push **/*.nupkg --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n```\n\n**Key differences:**\n| Before | After |\n|---|---|\n| `secrets.NUGET_API_KEY` | No secret needed |\n| No special permissions | `id-token: write` required |\n| Manual key rotation | Automatic OIDC token exchange |\n\n**3. Remove** the `NUGET_API_KEY` secret from your repo settings once verified.\n\n> **Note:** `dotnet nuget push` automatically detects the OIDC token from the GitHub Actions environment when no `--api-key` is provided and the NuGet source has a matching trusted publisher configured.\n\nWould you like me to update a specific workflow file?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"9213fc4a-c24e-4874-9208-d2066fc5e26e","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"There are no workflow files in the current directory. The user is asking a general question about switching from NuGet API key to trusted publishing (OIDC). Let me provide guidance based on my knowledge.","outputTokens":504,"requestId":"E3EB:86E8:1C83BCD:2005BC5:6A07BFDB"},"id":"a8a47a11-38da-4e79-acb3-0e60d6bc95ed","timestamp":"2026-05-16T00:52:54.609Z","parentId":"dc3c46f4-ea82-41f6-830f-69de2e8e4279"}
